Chapter 19. Acknowledgments

章 19. 致謝詞


This innocent little Frequently Asked Questions document has been written, rewritten, edited, folded, spindled, mutilated, 
eviscerated, contemplated, discombobulated, cogitated, regurgitated, rebuilt, castigated, and reinvigorated over the last 
decade, by a cast of hundreds if not thousands. Repeatedly.

這個合法的小型常見問題文檔已經被編寫，重寫，編輯，折疊，編組，殘缺，剔除，考慮，困惑，沉思，反芻，重建，鞭撻，並由數百甚至數千人的努力
，在過去的十年中重新振作起來。直至今日仍持續不斷。


We wish to thank every one of the people responsible, and we encourage you to join them in making this FAQ even better.
我們要感謝每一位負責人，我們鼓勵您加入他們，讓這個常見問答集變得更好。 
